channel.description:
The Grim Reaper of Death is a non-player character who appears at a player's death 

in your death method(Player.java) 
Add this (above death emote)

[code]Server.engine.newNPC(2862, this.absX-1, this.absY, this.heightLevel, 0, 0, 0, 0, false, 0);[/code]

If you get Errors on the first step try This 
[code]Server.engine.newNPC(2862, this.absX-1, this.absY, this.heightLevel, 0, 0, 0, 0, false, 0);[/code]


Next open NPC.java and add some variables

Undnder 
public class NPC {

[code] public int deathshow = -1;
    public int RandomMess = Misc.random(8);[/code]

